{"tid":150410,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"番工番到冇哂心機動力做野 想裸辭抖下","createTime":"2017-03-10T04:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T09:43:18.000Z","uid":38253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec7bac5e555f64bc9c9a1d10c7f04d6d72211c39","tid":150410,"uid":38253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:31:11.000Z","msg":"而家番緊5days工 chur就唔係好chur 同事都好好 但係就自己個心完全頹哂 完全冇動力做野<br />\n導火線係人工升幅非常不理想(腦細話個市差)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢排已不斷send cv, 但毫無音訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以而家係 份工幾好 但自己想抖 但裸辭驚搵唔到工<br />\n如果有offer先resign就工駁工 我驚自己頂唔順<br />\n定係繼續做住呢份 放番幾日假抖抖 有offer先遞信好<br />\n好苦惱 番工都唔知為乜 日日行屍走肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcabf38bcd9a1897a90265521506f00e78a313e1","tid":150410,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:34:01.000Z","msg":"我就是一個例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 裸辭去歐洲一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n間公司換左人越做越閪，做CS TEAM，原本3個人 走下一個走下又一個<br />\n最後得返我 仲要同事遞左信都冇即時出AD請人 到我遞埋信都冇出<br />\n真心垃圾公司"},{"pid":"c5eace72c28b508d78985c66052edfaf0743c54f","tid":150410,"uid":38253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:45:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我就是一個例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 裸辭去歐洲一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n間公司換左人越做越閪，做CS TEAM，原本3個人 走下一個走下又一個<br />\n最後得返我 仲要同事遞左信都冇即時出AD請人 到我遞埋信都冇出<br />\n真心垃圾公司</blockquote><br />\n係咪番黎香港就即刻搵工 定過多排先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6241569c732568d15f326e9c8eb4691d4cfc3c9b","tid":150410,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:49:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我就是一個例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 裸辭去歐洲一個月<img s