\n之後1 2月連埋過年勁唔好過 覺得自己好廢<br />\n好彩係新工係自己想做果行 由低做起都無所謂<br />\n我建議你無信心就諗清楚自己想點先辭<br />\n唔係空左咁耐你實後悔</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我最怕呢樣野<br />\n事實上封信我2月1已經print左出黎 擺檯頭準備boss番黎就遞比佢裸辭<br />\n但理性阻止左我呢下衝動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係果日之後 每日都行屍走肉 走又唔係唔走又唔係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea08045627741e7138b4c450b3ec14882b6f39e","tid":150410,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:15:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我裸辭去左2個月旅行<br />\n11月中返黎到2月尾先搵到工<br />\n頭2個月還好<br />\n之後1 2月連埋過年勁唔好過 覺得自己好廢<br />\n好彩係新工係自己想做果行 由低做起都無所謂<br />\n我建議你無信心就諗清楚自己想點先辭<br />\n唔係空左咁耐你實後悔</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我最怕呢樣野<br />\n事實上封信我2月1已經print左出黎 擺檯頭準備boss番黎就遞比佢裸辭<br />\n但理性阻止左我呢下衝動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係果日之後 每日都行屍走肉 走又唔係唔走又唔係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係咁 你搵到先走啦 <br />\n我呢家辭左唔係有旅行要去 有個緩衝區<br />\n唔係我都會好似你咁"},{"pid":"971aeec3fd15c0b52931e51297d75b86f1f68ea1","tid":150410,"uid":90389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T12:58:20.000Z","msg":"同樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c60db030b3c0c0e3bf08e1c4735382e01deb664","tid":150410,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T13:02:37.000Z","msg":"same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想裸辭 但係又未搵倒下一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b39e8d64bf884e74491d74f5c8ccf3a264e219","tid":150410,"uid":38253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T09:48:03.000Z","msg":"想遞信了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a29ec72e65d96afe7a019851e1b30271346f249","tid":150410,"uid":8848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:54:40.000Z","msg":"樓主遞左信未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0a20f66e15b0a1d23bcab5521f9e5af56cfc95","tid":150410,"uid":12991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:01:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我裸辭去左2個月旅行<br />\n11月中返黎到2月尾先搵到工<br />\n頭2個月還好<br />\n之後1 2月連埋過年勁唔好過 覺得自己好廢<br />\n好彩係新工係自己想做果行 由低做起都無所謂<br />\n我建議你無信心就諗清楚自己想點先辭<br />\n唔係空左咁耐你實後悔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時搵工都要識睇時機<br />\n年尾好多人等埋過年會少工<br />\n12月聖誕/ 新年公司都會過埋先請人<br />\n黎緊EASTER 都係<br />\n<br />\nON99 唔留意好多時咁就要坐2,3個月"},{"pid":"06087292fa67c35c5f662a6f7c4e279ab18b203f","tid":150410,"uid":38253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T09:19:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主遞左信未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遞左喇 但大佬想留我<br />\n而家傾緊有冇得加D 加到我就留啦"},{"pid":"2f2ad7b2d446ff614086aa056d295f3349f523e0","tid":150410,"uid":39317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T09:28:48.000Z","msg":"磨蝕哂<br />\n 但又無勇氣辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b1b6b6bdafb4cf2eef92e8225b86494e11489f","tid":150410,"uid":38253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T09:56:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>磨蝕哂<br />\n 但又無勇氣辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n番工真係好消磨意志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8536b67cacf73f2d010812b6c779b375a8ee8aa","tid":150410,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:18:07.000Z","msg":"I know that feel brother<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f2c4e8fbc6ecd1b718e634fb61e1a0ff3370a5","tid":150410,"uid":75637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:22:10.000Z","msg":"返左7個月，好想辭工，唔慣返工生活，加上呢份工唔係我想做嗰行，但又冇勇氣遞信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbccb83771dcc1e0f05ea517869f0847f6009aae","tid":150410,"uid":38253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:26:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>I know that feel brother<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb98fd8a95b782cab8072cfd80026ac70b62667f","tid":150410,"uid":38253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:27:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返左7個月，好想辭工，唔慣返工生活，加上呢份工唔係我想做嗰行，但又冇勇氣遞信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n襯早走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反正都唔會係呢行發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8172289165c1151e18a62e7236ac67681c14335","tid":150410,"uid":75637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:41:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>返左7個月，好想辭工，唔慣返工生活，加上呢份工唔係我想做嗰行，但又冇勇氣遞信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n襯早走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反正都唔會係呢行發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係freshgrad 第一份工做唔夠一年好似唔係幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1fc411482f4f593592f9da7d3d551683a24ec1","tid":150410,"uid":25044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T09:41:18.000Z","msg":"同你一樣 不過同事西 <br />\n加咗人工留我 但係加咗都係唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}